{"tid":2266091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"脫罪情侶：留低就要堅持","createTime":"2020-11-01T04:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T05:01:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b1c1f4487cbd9595a5e58bcf8c92efdb214dde","tid":2266091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/II5HCWBAMFEVTGT6CBJXAKCEDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FII5HCWBAMFEVTGT6CBJXAKCEDU%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=926e9431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FII5HCWBAMFEVTGT6CBJXAKCEDU%2F&h=8108c1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/II5HCWBAMFEVTGT6CBJXAKCEDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n脫罪情侶：留低就要堅持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s4aXV568-YYnuJL-zn5zAf9Dnl8=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OBM4UGQN3BBF3CGTQRM3Y4RKUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs4aXV568-YYnuJL-zn5zAf9Dnl8%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOBM4UGQN3BBF3CGTQRM3Y4RKUU.jpg&h=1f63ffdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余德穎與莫嘉晴（右）一同脫罪，昨牽手離開法庭。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】8.31灣仔暴動案中，一對相戀八年的情侶一同被捕、一同被控，最終一同脫罪，牽手一同步出法庭。兩人裁決後受訪，坦承被控暴動罪後感到不安甚至變得懦弱，但他們仍會以不同方式堅持。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：8.31暴動案 7被告無罪  官：穿黑衣不等於參與 逃跑或因怕警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「警察指控全部生安白造」<br />\n<br />\n同為24歲的余德穎及莫嘉晴昨同受訪。余憶述開審前一周始得悉控方證據內容，「見到警察對我嘅指控，全部都係假嘅、生安白造，你就覺得全部係為咗鋤死你而作出呢啲證據」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。她希望香港人「唔好輸畀恐懼」，亦坦言起初因為被控變得懦弱，「佢哋如果要搞，實揀啲有暴動罪嘅人嚟搞」。惟她相信很多人仍然堅持，只是每人方式不同，「留低嘅就要堅持」。<br />\n<br />\n兩人本來曾談婚論嫁，但捲入暴動案後，莫自言「人生好似停頓咗咁，冇可能有任何規劃，唔可以搵長工，就算想買iPhone都唔會買，可能只係用三個月。𠵱家都唔會諗結婚，唔想結完婚分開六年」。莫稱裁決前一晚難以入睡，「好想把握最後嘅時間咁，喺度碌電話上網，唔捨得瞓」。他們滿意裁決，不過仍擔心律政司會上訴；現時最想回家餵貓，余更興奮地說：「我哋可以養多隻啦！」"},{"pid":"38dacf0b49ec1e5cfcddbdc42dddee55f2d34db2","tid":2266091,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea46efeb05f404580bfd9dc92ab1d0b0ac86d30","tid":2266091,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38dacf0b49ec1e5cfcddbdc42dddee55f2d34db2","tid":2266091,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41cf4b918aa45dd5f31c715a6063a0b90aee25c","tid":2266091,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1dd02da548b53618d9da09c8e065979af135a8","tid":2266091,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ba676ba8cdb5fcfdbfaaa656636f17bea86241","tid":2266091,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"撐住呀"},{"pid":"16fedd790f9f497367e6e1aa2114a25cb380b747","tid":2266091,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"請懲罰佢哋間IG shop <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/yolostore.hk?igshid=1bnq8s8di8kop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyolostore.hk%3Figshid%3D1bnq8s8di8kop&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj